# Redesign Verification: Technical Tab

## Task Checklist
- [x] Open http://localhost:3000/technical
- [x] Scroll and verify centering of equation blocks
- [x] Screenshot '01 — Quadrotor Dynamics' and '02 — State & Control Formulation'
- [!] Verify hover logic for variables and screenshot hover state (**FAILED**: No panel appears on hover, JS search found no related elements)
- [x] Check '08 — Theoretical Guarantee' for color highlighting and screenshot
